{"tid":375310,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救)壞底板, 買新底板前一問","createTime":"2017-08-26T12:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T06:14:32.000Z","uid":33437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81a52f58c670f6d011ca752a1df279c88dc30d47","tid":375310,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/233532_b2aa278cfdc69ae8ae098efc4f7e93cf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F233532_b2aa278cfdc69ae8ae098efc4f7e93cf.jpeg&h=7514f9f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舊機配置如上, 壞左底板, 只想買返張全新, 夾返其他舊硬件用, 普通上網唔打機。<br />\n<br />\n我知底板要買LGA 1155 socket, 但仲有以下問題:<br />\n1.我想用內置顯示卡, 點睇張底板支唔支援?<br />\n   係唔係只要張卡有埋VGA/HDMI等mon插頭就代表ok?<br />\n<br />\n2.ATX箱裝M.ATX底板係唔係都無問題?因為張卡反而細左。<br />\n<br />\n3.買底板仲有冇其他特別野要注意?<br />\n   我知要睇Ram(1600), SATA/SATA 3插頭數量。<br />\n   CPU (nm), 火牛插頭類型洗唔洗額外留意?<br />\n<br />\n這兩張卡是否都無問題?<br />\nASUS 華碩 H61M-K H61,DDR3,LGA 1155,M.ATX M/B<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asus.com/Motherboards/H61MK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asus.com%2FMotherboards%2FH61MK%2F&d=t%2BplOLL2VS0IivlVUNRgLhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=8236feb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asus.com/Motherboards/H61MK/</a><br />\nGIGABYTE 技嘉 GA-H61M-DS2 R5 H61,DDR3,LGA 1155,M.ATX M/B 全固態電容<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gigabyte.tw/Motherboard/GA-H61M-DS2-rev-50#ov\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gigabyte.tw%2FMotherboard%2FGA-H61M-DS2-rev-50%23ov&d=t%2BplOLL2VS0IivlVUNRgLhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=b1d282dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gigabyte.tw/Motherboard/GA-H61M-DS2-rev-50#ov</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406e300ba61714bd066222fd7e4b93b903521910","tid":375310,"ui