5或者Z77全新既賣<br />\n<br />\n但係牌子未必係你想要<br />\n<br />\n得BIOSTAR,ECS果類"},{"pid":"20870ce92d8bc108a322756dab2511a464ba283f","tid":375310,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>底版插到用到無問題<br />\n<br />\n但係down左grade.<br />\n<br />\n1155果時H61無原生sata3<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔介意既就唔係問題<br />\n<br />\n不過你依加買要幾錢塊?要400-500既話就算啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買塊H77二手都係200<br />\n<br />\n但係起碼spec接近.但係始終二手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有d舖頭其實仲有B75或者Z77全新既賣<br />\n<br />\n但係牌子未必係你想要<br />\n<br />\n得BIOSTAR,ECS果類</blockquote><br />\n買塊全新,上到網就算 ,H61差不多要$400<br />\nB75大牌子大舖無哂貨。<br />\n<br />\n同埋update bios洗唔洗去代理?<br />\n定係去買底板間電腦舖會幫我update埋?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}